text: Katalin Sarlós (born 24 August 1968) is a Hungarian rower. She competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Hungary Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Budapest
